summary: All three requirements are implemented. REQ-1 is satisfied by the new MusicPage.tsx and MusicTrackCard.tsx with a responsive grid of track cards linking to https://suno.com/@nebacrypt. REQ-2 is satisfied by the music preview section added to LandingPage.tsx showing 3 featured tracks and a 'Se all musikk' CTA navigating to /music. REQ-3 is satisfied by the music route registered in App.tsx and the 'Musikk' nav link added to Header.tsx for both desktop and mobile menus with active state styling. All acceptance criteria appear to be met.
